title: Dak Prescott, Ben Roethlisberger, Baker Mayfield, & Aaron Rodgers
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Ben Roethlisberger, Baker Mayfield, & Aaron Rodgers
description:
Colin discusses what will happen if the Dallas Cowboys beat the New Orleans Saints tonight, Pittsburgh Steelers QB Ben Roethlisberger throwing his teammates under the bus, why people will get burned out on Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield, and more on Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers. Guests include Chris Broussard, Greg Cosell, Daryl Johnston, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
